      "item": "parse_tree_path",
      "reviewed": true,
      "intent": "Nom parser combinator for parsing a complete tree_path into a TreePath struct. Handles :: delimited segments and injection markers attached directly to the preceding segment (name//lang) without requiring a :: separator.",
